| Episodes stored | 948 |
| Episodes extracted | 948 |
| Extraction calls | 948 |
| Embedding calls | 0 |
| Recall calls | 500 |
| Reader calls | 500 |
| Total ingest time | 4796.6s |
| Total query time | 1486.3s |

## Error Analysis

- **Best category**: abstention (96.7%)
- **Worst category**: knowledge-update (2.8%)

